d6 10. h3 {White prepares Be3, but this is kind of slow.} O-O 11. Be3 Nc6 12.
Ne1 Nd7 13. f4 Bf6 {Black is doing great.} 14. Rc1 Bd4 15. Qd2 Bxe3+ 16. Qxe3
