{A very convincing win by Black} 1. c4 e5 2. Nc3 Bb4 3. e4 {Pretty much the
only move where we don't capture on c3 immediately.} Nc6 4. a3 (4. g3 {After
such a move we would play} d6 {planning Nge7-f5}) 4... Bxc3 {Now, things have
changed. We can afford to take on c3 as it comes with a free tempo.} 5. bxc3 d6
6. d3 f5 $1 {opening up our pieces.} 7. Nf3 fxe4 {We can't go with ...f4 right
now, as we are "under-developed"} 8. dxe4 Nf6 9. Qd3 O-O 10. h3 Qe8 {planning
Qg6, Nd7-Nc5 and Na5.} 11. Bg5 Be6 (11... Nd7 {would have been a better choice,
planning Nc5.}) 12. Bxf6 Rxf6 13. Be2 Qg6 14. g4 Raf8 15. Rf1 Na5 16. Nd2 Qg5
17. f3 Qh4+ 18. Kd1 Qxh3 19. Kc2 Qh6 20. Rh1 Qf4 21. Rag1 R6f7 22. Rh5 g6 23.
Rh4 Rd7 24. Bf1 c6 25. Qe2 d5 26. Qe1 dxc4 27. Rgh1 Rfd8 28. R1h2 Qg5 29. f4
Qxf4 30. Rf2 Qg5 31. Nf3 Qe7 32. Nxe5 Rd1 0-1

