Black has a perfect game with ..g5 - ... h5 or ..Rfc8 plans.}) 8... Nc6 9. d4
Be7 10. e3 O-O 11. Bd2 a6 12. Na4 Nd7 13. Rc1 Rc8 14. a3 b5 15. Nc5 Nxc5 (15...
