18. Qxf3 Ne5 19. Qe2 Nc4 $15 {Black has an amazing knight on c3 and good
center control.}) 16. dxc5 Ne5 17. b4 Nc4 18. a4 Nb2 19. Qb3 Nxa4 20. e4 dxe4
0-1

