{This course offer a repertoire for Black against the Reti/English line, based
on the Nimzo-Indian spirit:} 1. Nf3 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 ({The one theory file
pertains to} 3. e3 {Still, it's an understanding-based type of line all the
same.}) 3... Bb4 {We deal with minor moves as well as major options like} 4.
Qc2 {What's important, the whole reprtoire is based almost solely on
understanding and not concrete memorization, which is why there is only one
theory file, and the course is primarily comprised of model games explaining
Black's ideas.} ({and} 4. g4 $5) *

