{In this section we deal with the big main move:} 1. Nf3 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3
Bb4 4. Qc2 {Our main response is} d6 5. a3 Bxc3 6. Qxc3 e5 {Planning to
develop the bishop via the c8-h3 diagonal, not b7, which is less promising.} ({
Or first} 6... O-O) ({Or even} 6... a5 $5 {In either case we strive for the
same setup.}) *

