trade in this version is not so bad for him, but in fact is worse than if he
had just played Nxf5.} 17. Qd1 Nc4 18. b3 Nd6 $17 19. Bh3 Qh4 20. Kg2 Rae8 21.
Rc1 Ndf7 {Black makes creative use of the f7-square.} 22. Rc2 $2 {Falling into
