$5) 11. e3 Bxf3 12. gxf3 Nd4 13. Qd1 Qg5 $19 (13... Nf4 $19)) 6. Nf3 (6. e3 d5
$5 $36 {This is a very nice Reversed Sicilian for Black!} (6... O-O) 7. cxd5
Nxd5 8. Qc2 O-O 9. d3 Re8 (9... Bg4)) 6... Qe7 $5 {As we can see, we have very
easy play with several logical moves!} (6... d6 $5 7. d3 Bg4 $132) 7. d3 d5 $36
) (4. e3 $6 O-O 5. Nf3 Re8 {More flexible than ...Nc6, since we keep the
option of playing ...c6-d5.} 6. a3 $2 {This is way too slow! Black will be
