9... d5 10. cxd5 b6 $17) 4... Qe7 $5 {Once again you don't need to know much -
just develop your pieces and play a nice unclear game! For example,} (4... d6
$2 {SUPER SOS!! THIS IS A VERY TYPICAL MISTAKE TO REMEMBER!} 5. Qa4+ $3 Nc6 6.
