7. Qxd8+ Kxd8 8. Be3 $14 b6 $2 9. O-O-O+ Ke7 10. Bb5 $16) 7. Bg5 (7. cxd6 cxd6
{with a playable position for Black.} ({After} 7... Nxe4 {White has} 8. Nxe5 $1
Nxe5 9. Qa4+ Bd7 10. Qxe4 $14)) 7... h6 8. Bxf6 Qxf6 9. cxd6 cxd6 {Black got
an equal, playable position out of the opening.} 10. Bc4 Bg4 11. Qd3 Bxf3 12.
gxf3 O-O 13. O-O-O Rfd8 14. Kb1 Ne7 $1 {[%csl Ge7,Rf4][%cal Ye7g6,Yg6f4] The
