White should have captured with the knight.} 11. Nxd5 Nxd5 12. Bxd5 Bxd5 13.
Qxd5 {Black has a weakness on d6, but White is far behind in development.} (13.
cxd5 e4 $17 {[%csl Gc5,Gd3,Ge5,Gf3][%cal Yd7e5,Yd7c5,Yc5d3,Ye5d3,Ye5f3]}) 13...
Nf6 $1 (13... Nb6 14. Qd3 $11 (14. Qxd6 $2 Qxd6 15. Rxd6 Nxc4 $17)) 14. Qxd6
Qa5+ 15. b4 Qxa2 $17) 11... Bg4 (11... Bf5 $15 {This is even better than ...
Bg4 - Black wants to continue with ...Nc5.} 12. e4 Bg6 13. Nge2 b5 {Black is
taking over the initiative.} 14. a3 a5 $17 15. f3 b4 (15... Qb6)) 12. f3 {
This is quite useful for White.} Bh5 13. e4 Ne8 $2 14. h4 h6 15. Nge2 $16 {
[%csl Rh5]} b5 16. g4 b4 17. Nb1 Bg6 18. h5 Bh7 19. Qxb4 Rb8 20. Qd2 a5 21.
