1. c4 e5 2. g3 c6 3. Nf3 d6 4. Bg2 f5 5. Nc3 Nf6 (5... Be7 6. O-O g5 {can be
tried in blitz games, though it is not good objectively.}) 6. O-O a5 $1 ({
I tried to make} 6... g6 {work, but it does not seem to equalize.} 7. d3 Bg7 8.
e4 $14 Na6 9. exf5 gxf5 10. d4 e4 11. Ng5 O-O 12. Nh3 d5 13. Qb3 Qb6 14. Be3
Qxb3 15. axb3 dxc4 16. bxc4 Ng4 17. Nf4 Nb4 18. Rac1 Rd8 19. Rfd1 Kf7 20. h3
Nxe3 21. fxe3 Bh6 22. Nce2 Be6 23. Bf1 Kf6 24. Kf2 Bf7 25. g4 Bg5 26. Bg2 Bh4+
27. Kg1 Bg6 28. Rf1 Re8 29. gxf5 Bxf5 30. Nh5+ Kg6 31. Ng7 Kxg7 32. Rxf5 Nd3
33. Rcf1 Re7 34. Rh5 Be1 35. Rg5+ Kh8 36. Nf4 Bd2 37. Rg3 Nxb2 38. Kf2 Nxc4 39.
Ke2 Rg8 40. Rxg8+ Kxg8 41. Nh5 Bxe3 42. Nf6+ Kg7 43. Nxe4 b5 44. Ng3 Bxd4+ 45.
Kd3 Rd7 46. Nf5+ Kg6 47. Be4 Bf6+ 48. Kc2 Rd2+ 49. Kb1 Rb2+ 50. Kc1 Bg5+ 51.
Kd1 Nd2 52. Ne7+ Kh5 53. Rf2 Nxe4 54. Rxb2 Bxe7) 7. d4 e4 8. Nh4 Rg8 $1 $40 9.
f3 $1 {This is connected to a piece sacrifice.} (9. f4 d5 $17 10. cxd5 cxd5 11.
Bh3 g6 12. Ng2 Nc6 13. Ne3 Be6 $19) (9. Bh3 $2 g5 $1 10. Nxf5 (10. Ng2 g4)
10... g4 $19) 9... g5 10. Nxf5 $1 Bxf5 11. fxe4 Bc8 $5 $13 {Black is a piece
up though White has sufficient compensation - later he managed to win.} 0-1

